OL,4,CPeople may quit if forced to work from
OL,5,Chome, Rishi Sunak warns
OL,6, The chancellor has warned bosses that
OL,7, staff may quit if they are not allowed
OL,8, to work from the office as the UK
OL,9, emerges from lockdown.
OL,11,FRishi Sunak told the Telegraph that
OL,12,Femployees would "vote with their feet"
OL,13,Fand could consider leaving for a rival
OL,14,Fif made to work from home full time.
OL,16,FA number of companies have announced
OL,17,Fplans to close offices prompting fears
OL,18,Ffor city centres.
OL,20,FBut now the chancellor has urged firms
OL,21,Fnot to abandon the office altogether.
